{"tid":1164430,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我地波台手足全心一意撐慕容，反bob叔","createTime":"2019-05-21T05:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T11:59:32.000Z","uid":134997,"like":29,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"73a3c32445372a9bdb68bca636a0c56c67fd47f2","tid":1164430,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"bob叔依啲有錢佬就高高在上，就睇唔起我地啲死窮鬼，知唔知有幾多人因為窮所以無能力讀大學，只可以靠自己早啲出嚟努力搵錢，小花就係小花，啲有錢囝淨係識一味叫人讀書先賺到錢，無諗過無錢無資源就讀唔成書，不如早啲做野仲好<br />\n<br />\n幕容就唔同，佢係靠佢自己努力上位，靠佢打機勁+講野叻先搵到錢，你可以話佢無讀過書先會叫人唔讀書，但絕對唔能夠忽視佢努力💪🏼<br />\n<br />\nBOB叔正一食屎狗，溫室小花，叫我地啲死窮鬼去讀書，何不食肉糜"},{"pid":"b051a24eb518ada274ee20743ec6c8244ad9a241","tid":1164430,"uid":134997,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"扑叔我屌你老母！"},{"pid":"0f0fdba24d05ef46d657b760c7cc6b03e1b398d4","tid":1164430,"uid":134997,"like":5,"dislike":12,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"負皮我嘅一定係溫室小花，私樓仔，無諗過我地係處於咩嘅環境先會咁嘅諗法<br />\n今日，我們都是慕容公子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6433a2d7d31641fcb078735658948bb51ea3c25","tid":1164430,"uid":134997,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"負評我嘅人駁唔撚到？"},{"pid":"5c762c22fa39fe3daf36b4e46a9f2e98a33c103d","tid":1164430,"uid":153,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"撐左達哥先"},{"pid":"9bb46fd28ca079b59884e981adc70c223437ae73","tid":1164430,"uid":78785,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"曲到直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eccdc1accdd1056a7e4a96ddf40a1498864e6fb","tid":1164430,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"我撐大理=,="},{"pid":"25b824b150e02e4cd226cfab39dc4dfb128d34cf",